OL,3,CPolice officer admits causing death by
OL,4,Ccareless driving following fatal crash
OL,6,FA police officer has pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fcausing death by careless driving,
OL,8,Ffollowing a collision in Gateshead in
OL,9,Fwhich a 74-year-old woman died.
OL,11,FBut 56-year-old PC Mark Roberts denied
OL,12,Fthe more serious charge of causing
OL,13,Fdeath by dangerous driving, in
OL,14,Frelation to the crash near the
OL,15,FMetroCentre in July 2022.
OL,17,FMuriel Pinkney died from the injuries
OL,18,Fshe sustained in the crash. She was
OL,19,Fthe passenger on a motorbike which
OL,20,Fcollided with a marked police vehicle
OL,21,Fon Dunston Road.
