OL,3,CPolice officer admits causing death by
OL,4,Ccareless driving following fatal crash
OL,6,FReporter Kris Jepson has been at
OL,7,FDurham Crown Court
OL,9,FMeanwhile, Roberts also admitted
OL,10,Fcausing serious injury to 77-year-old
OL,11,FRonald Pinkney by careless driving. He
OL,12,Fwas riding the motorbike at the time
OL,13,Fof the crash.
OL,15,FRoberts also denied the more serious
OL,16,Fcharge of causing serious injury to Mr
OL,17,FPinkney by dangerous driving.
