OL,3,CPolice officer admits causing death by
OL,4,Ccareless driving following fatal crash
OL,6,FRoberts, wearing a suit and overcoat,
OL,7,Fappeared at Durham Crown Court this
OL,8,Fmorning (Friday 17 January) to admit
OL,9,Fthe two charges and to enter not
OL,10,Fguilty pleas to the other two.
OL,12,FThe Northumbria Police officer, who
OL,13,Flives in Darlington, was told that the
OL,14,Fprosecution intended to proceed to
OL,15,Ftrial on the two charges that he
OL,16,Fdenies.
OL,18,FA five-day trial date was
OL,19,Fprovisionally set for May 2026 and he
OL,20,Fwas granted unconditional bail.
